recent_articles.title: 'Magnificent Seven' stocks: Buy Nvidia, skip Apple
recent_articles.summary:
The "Magnificent Seven," Nvidia (NVDA), Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), Tesla (TSLA), Microsoft (MSFT), Amazon (AMZN), Meta (META), and Apple (AAPL), have dominated the markets over the last couple of years. But which one should you buy? In the latest Good Buy or Goodbye, GraniteShares Founder & CEO Will Rhind says Nvidia should be added to your portfolio, while Apple is one to skip, for now.
